A)—head and pronotum dark piceous brown to black. Elytra chestnut brown, with diffuse piceous patches around shoulders, along suture, over elytral intervals 
<number box="[700,752,1480,1504]" pageId="1" pageNumber="472" value="9.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="8.0">8-10</number>
